 ("Combining insurance + financing", "Patients regularly use insurance to cover the diagnostic and restorative portion of treatment, then use Beautifi for cosmetic or elective parts (whitening, <a href='/services/cosmetic-dentistry/'>veneers</a>, Invisalign). Together, you get the smile you want with predictable monthly payments."),
